318
00:22:36,300 --> 00:22:37,600
Nan Nan,

319
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:39,600
Hongdou is here to visit you.

320
00:22:40,500 --> 00:22:42,200
Are you happy?

321
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:24,700
