362
00:25:04,600 --> 00:25:06,500
Here's the pretty aunty.

363
00:25:06,500 --> 00:25:09,500
Finger heart! Finger heart.

364
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,900
This wine is made by her.

365
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:14,000
It's really tasty.

366
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,100
This is made from sour grapes, right?

367
00:25:15,100 --> 00:25:17,000
Yes, but the wine isn't sour.

368
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:21,200
