00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:10,200
<i>who's going to buy it?</i>

388
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:13,200
<i>This isn't carved. It's real.</i>

389
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:14,600
<i>Trying to scare me?</i>

390
00:26:14,600 --> 00:26:17,100
<i>I'm not. These are real.</i>

391
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,900
<i>- Imp!</i>
- <i>Wait, Master.</i>

392
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:24,000
<i>I just wanted to add a dish for you.</i>

393
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,600
<i>They're nutritious!</i>
- <i>Stop, please!</i>

394
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:26,600
