408
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:33,200
Has she had a meal?

409
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:35,400
Of course, she has.

410
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:38,000
- Ask her.
- Ask what?

411
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:40,000
Ask her what she ate.

412
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,000
