416
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:53,400
If you aren't going to keep in touch, change this.

417
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:56,200
Fine, I'll change it later.

418
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:59,600
You're not a shred like me.

