424
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,000
I'm not like that.

425
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:17,600
I merely fell in love with your grandpa.

426
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:19,400
I'm not like you.

427
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:22,100
