623
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:05,500
We were silent at home.

624
00:41:05,500 --> 00:41:08,500
We turned on the television, but no one was watching it.

625
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:11,400
When we missed her,

626
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:15,400
