627
00:41:16,500 --> 00:41:19,000
When we were exhausted from crying, we'd go to bed.

628
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:23,400
It was like a nightmare.

629
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:25,400
Nothing felt real.

630
00:41:28,500 --> 00:41:32,200
Our relatives and neighbors

631
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:36,900
