632
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:41,700
They cried with us.

633
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:45,600
We were only afraid of others prying.

634
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:52,300
Hongdou,

635
00:41:56,400 --> 00:42:01,600
I always wonder if I was an evil person in my past life.

636
